BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:n7IsmgS5e0JGaJxQr8qPn
SUMMARY:University Awards Ceremony and Reception 2027
DTSTAMP:20260630T135114Z
DTSTART:20270427T210000Z
DESCRIPTION:The entire campus community is invited to join us as we celebra
	te teaching at Rice and—in particular—those instructors who care very deep
	ly about student learning. There will be a wine and appetizer reception fo
	llowing the ceremony. All students\, faculty\, alumni\, and staff are enco
	uraged to attend!  Please RSVP here: https://bit.ly/cte_RSVP (https://bit.
	ly/cte_RSVP).Awards To Be PresentedGeorge R. Brown Prize for Excellence in
	 Teaching  George R. Brown Awards for Superior Teaching  Nicolas Salgo Out
	standing Teaching Award  Trenton W. Wann Award for Excellence in Teaching 
	and Mentorship  Charles W. Duncan\, Jr. Achievement Award for Outstanding 
	Faculty  Sophia Meyer Farb Prize for Teaching (Phi Beta Kappa Teaching Awa
	rd)  Exceptional Scholar Award for Sustained Excellence  Jack Gill Award f
	or Innovation and Entrepreneurship Excellence  Marjorie Corcoran Award  Pr
	ovost's Award for Outstanding Faculty Achievement  Provost's Award for Out
	standing Early-Career Achievement  Provost's Award for Outstanding Doctora
	l Advisor  Presidential Award for Mentoring  Rice University Faculty Award
	 for Excellence in Research\, Teaching\, and Service  Rice University Facu
	lty Award for Excellence in Professional Service and Leadership  Rice Univ
	ersity Faculty Award for Excellence in University Service and Leadership  
	Sarah A. Burnett Teaching Prize in the Social Sciences  Sarofim Professor 
	for Distinguished Teaching in the Humanities  Award for Outstanding Teachi
	ng in the School of Natural Sciences  Award for Excellence in Teaching in 
	the School of Engineering  Graduate Liberal Studies John Freeman Awards  G
	raduate Teaching Awards  Student-Taught Course Teaching Awards\n\nhttps://
	events.rice.edu/cte/event/university-awards-ceremony-and-reception-2027\n\
	nFrom Rice University - Open to the Public
URL:https://events.rice.edu/cte/event/university-awards-ceremony-and-recept
	ion-2027
